WEBVTT

00:01:57.520 --> 00:02:00.160
like I have some from the two of you.

00:02:00.560 --> 00:02:02.720
And these are important today

00:02:02.760 --> 00:02:04.880
because these expectations
are the foundation



00:02:04.880 --> 00:02:07.510
on which we build the rest of our lives.

00:02:07.540 --> 00:02:10.760
Your grandmother had decided
that her son would be well educated.

00:02:10.800 --> 00:02:13.990
She always said that,
and will tell you as well,

00:02:14.070 --> 00:02:18.280
that education is not just
collection of knowledge,

00:02:18.280 --> 00:02:24.200
it is about the dedication, discipline and
hard work that goes into garnering it --

00:02:24.200 --> 00:02:26.880
that is the real education.

